snippet.title: lure_official_trailer_video
snippet.description:
Hello Survivors!

This is the official trailer video of the Lure. The countdown is started! Lure will be available on Steam in a few weeks! Feel free to share your ideas or suggestion on Discord or any other social media platforms. 

If you haven't seen already these leaks you can inspect them.
- First leak;

- Second leak;
